nodes.text: Dewall Paez was a male Human who lived on Tatooine during the Galactic Civil War and leader of the Wayfar spies. Circa 1 ABY, the Wayfar spies were recruited by Bib Fortuna, Jabba the Hutt's majordomo, to spy Romo Vax. Fortuna suspected Vax to double cross Jabba's organisation. However, Romo Vax managed to lure one of Bib Fortuna's henchman and made him assassinate Dewall Paez and some other Wayfar spies.

Dewall Paez appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
